From 6ad50c82e105cc9bc1a55cd7158430877061686e Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Joel Selvaraj <foss@joelselvaraj.com>
Date: Tue, 28 Apr 2026 11:40:03 -0500
Subject: [PATCH 180/194] sdm845.config: split into misc.config, pmos.config
 and sdm845.config

This is to make it easy to use in combination with pmb kconfig generate and envkernel builds, so both stays in sync.

Signed-off-by: Joel Selvaraj <foss@joelselvaraj.com>
---
 arch/arm64/configs/misc.config   | 111 ++++++++
 arch/arm64/configs/pmos.config   | 470 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 arch/arm64/configs/sdm845.config | 468 +-----------------------------
 3 files changed, 596 insertions(+), 453 deletions(-)
 create mode 100644 arch/arm64/configs/misc.config
 create mode 100644 arch/arm64/configs/pmos.config

